OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783639966
OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FThe man who organised live screenings
OL,8,Fof the Egypt vs Argentina World Cup
OL,9,Fgame in Gaza was killed by an Israeli
OL,10,Fstrike just before kick off, as ITV
OL,11,FNews Digital Video Producer Dan Ajose
OL,12,Freports
OL,14,FAn Israeli strike has killed a
OL,15,FPalestinian aid official who helped
OL,16,Forganise public screenings of a World
OL,17,FCup match across Gaza.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783639966
OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FThe strike, which happened just before
OL,8,Fkickoff of the Egypt-Argentina game on
OL,9,FTuesday, killed Mohamed al-Wahidi, an
OL,10,Fofficial with the Egyptian
OL,11,Fgovernment's relief arm in Gaza.
OL,13,FWahidi had been in a taxi on the way
OL,14,Fto a screening of the match in Tel al-
OL,15,FHawa in southern Gaza City when the
OL,16,Fmissile hit the car he was in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783639966
OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FThree others were killed in the
OL,8,Fattack, including driver Ahmed
OL,9,FDaghmush, 33, and two brothers, 10-
OL,10,Fyear-old Hamza al-Deri and 8-year-old
OL,11,FFar, according to Dr Mohamed Abu
OL,12,FSelmiya, the director of Shifa
OL,13,FHospital.
OL,15,FThe Israeli military said Wahidi, was
OL,16,Fnot a target of the strike and that
OL,17,Fthe attack was aimed at a Hamas
OL,18,Fmilitant and that it was checking
OL,19,Fwhether the driver, Daghmush, was the
OL,20,Ftarget.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783639966
OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FAbu Selmiya said Daghmush was a taxi
OL,8,Fdriver without any known links to
OL,9,Fmilitant groups.
OL,11,FIt turned what was supposed to be a
OL,12,Fmoment of celebration ` the live
OL,13,Fscreening of a potential upset against
OL,14,FArgentina by an Arab team ` into a
OL,15,Freminder of how the near-daily Israeli
OL,16,Fstrikes are continuing to kill
OL,17,Fcivilians despite a truce reached in
OL,18,FOctober.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
