PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783639966
OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FThe committee for which Wahidi worked
OL,8,Fis the relief arm of the Egyptian
OL,9,Fgovernment, which provides food,
OL,10,Fshelter and other assistance to
OL,11,FPalestinians in Gaza.
OL,13,FMany in the Palestinian diaspora live
OL,14,Facross the border in Egypt, which was
OL,15,Fa key mediator of the Israel-Hamas
OL,16,Fceasefire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
