PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783639966
OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FEgypt's Gaza fan base has grown since
OL,8,Fthe start of the World Cup tournament,
OL,9,Fwith coach Hossam Hassan spotlighting
OL,10,Fthe plight of the Palestinian people
OL,11,Fin press briefings and on the pitch.
OL,13,FHe dedicated his team's victory over
OL,14,FAustralia on Friday to both Egyptians
OL,15,Fand Palestinians and waved a
OL,16,FPalestinian flag.
OL,18,FIn a Monday briefing before the match
OL,19,Fagainst Argentina, Hassan urged the
OL,20,Fworld to do more for the Palestinian
OL,21,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783639966
OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,F"I urge you, I urge all media
OL,8,Fofficers, all athletes worldwide,
OL,9,Fregardless of their identities, maybe
OL,10,Fwe can convey a collective message
OL,11,Fthat is as follows, let the
OL,12,FPalestinian people be, let them exist,
OL,13,Flet them live a life of their own," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
