OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783639966
OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FIn the months since the ceasefire,
OL,8,FIsraeli attacks have killed at least
OL,9,F1,084 people, including nine killed by
OL,10,Fstrikes and gunfire across Gaza on
OL,11,FWednesday, according to local health
OL,12,Fofficials.
OL,14,FAmong the dead were two children, as
OL,15,Fwell as a truck driver who was gunned
OL,16,Fdown at a roadblock along the
OL,17,FPhiladelphi Corridor, an Israeli-
OL,18,Fcontrolled strip of land that runs
OL,19,Falong Gaza's border with Egypt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783639966
OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FThe Israeli military said it shot the
OL,8,Ftruck driver after he "ran towards the
OL,9,Ftroops." Another man was killed on the
OL,10,Fstreet by a drone in Gaza City.
OL,12,FIsrael's military says its strikes
OL,13,Ftarget militants and it regrets harm
OL,14,Fto civilians. Five Israeli soldiers
OL,15,Fhave been killed since the ceasefire
OL,16,Fwent into effect in October.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
