OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FThe Palestinian death toll from the
OL,8,FIsrael-Hamas war stands at 73,110,
OL,9,Faccording to the Gaza Health Ministry,
OL,10,Fwhich is part of the Hamas-led
OL,11,Fgovernment and is staffed by medical
OL,12,Fprofessionals who maintain detailed
OL,13,Frecords viewed as generally reliable
OL,14,Fby United Nations agencies and
OL,15,Findependent experts. It does not
OL,16,Fdistinguish between civilians and
OL,17,Fmilitants but says women and children
OL,18,Fmake up around half of all fatalities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
