OL,3,CAid official who organised World Cup
OL,4,Cscreening in Gaza killed in Israeli
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FThe war began when Hamas-led militants
OL,8,Fattacked southern Israel on Oct. 7,
OL,9,F2023, killing around 1,200 people and
OL,10,Ftaking 251 others hostage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
